        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- About Us Section -->
<section class="about-us" id="about-usid">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>About Hope Clinic</h2>
            <p>Your trusted partner in dental health since 2005</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text">
                <p>Hope Clinic is a state-of-the-art dental practice dedicated to providing exceptional dental care in a comfortable and welcoming environment. Our mission is to help patients achieve and maintain optimal oral health through personalized treatment plans and education.</p>
                <p>With our team of experienced dentists and dental professionals, cutting-edge technology, and patient-centered approach, we're committed to making every dental visit a positive experience.</p>
                <p>At Hope Clinic, we believe that a healthy smile contributes to overall well-being, and we're passionate about helping our patients achieve their best smile.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="~/images/images2/Slide2.jpg" alt="Hope Clinic Team">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="faq">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p>Find answers to common questions about our services</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-tabs">
            <div class="faq-tab">
                <input type="checkbox" id="faq1" class="faq-checkbox">
                <label for="faq1" class="faq-label">
                    How often should I visit the dentist?
                    <span class="faq-arrow"></span>
                </label>
                <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>Most patients should visit the dentist every six months for a check-up and professional cleaning. However, your dentist may recommend more frequent visits based on your specific oral health needs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-tab">
                <input type="checkbox" id="faq2" class="faq-checkbox">
                <label for="faq2" class="faq-label">
                    What should I do in a dental emergency?
                    <span class="faq-arrow"></span>
                </label>
                <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>If you're experiencing a dental emergency such as severe pain, swelling, bleeding, or a knocked-out tooth, contact our office immediately. We offer emergency dental services and will provide guidance on what to do until you can be seen.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-tab">
                <input type="checkbox" id="faq3" class="faq-checkbox">
                <label for="faq3" class="faq-label">
                    Do you accept dental insurance?
                    <span class="faq-arrow"></span>
                </label>
                <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>Yes, we accept most major dental insurance plans. Our administrative team will help you understand your coverage and maximize your benefits. We also offer payment plans for those without insurance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-tab">
                <input type="checkbox" id="faq4" class="faq-checkbox">
                <label for="faq4" class="faq-label">
                    How can I manage dental anxiety?
                    <span class="faq-arrow"></span>
                </label>
                <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>We understand that dental anxiety is common. Our team is trained to provide gentle care and can offer various comfort measures including sedation options, distraction techniques, and a calm environment to help you feel at ease during your visit.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-tab">
                <input type="checkbox" id="faq5" class="faq-checkbox">
                <label for="faq5" class="faq-label">
                    What age should children start seeing a dentist?
                    <span class="faq-arrow"></span>
                </label>
                <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>Children should have their first dental visit by their first birthday or when their first tooth appears. Early dental visits help establish good oral hygiene habits and can prevent future dental problems.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-tab">
                <input type="checkbox" id="faq6" class="faq-checkbox">
                <label for="faq6" class="faq-label">
                    How can I improve my smile?
                    <span class="faq-arrow"></span>
                </label>
                <div class="faq-content">
                    <p>We offer various cosmetic dental treatments including teeth whitening, veneers, bonding, and orthodontics to enhance your smile. During a consultation, our dentists can recommend the best options based on your goals and oral health.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
            <h2>Ready to Schedule Your Visit?</h2>
            <p>Take the first step towards a healthier smile today.</p>
            <a asp-controller="PatientHome" asp-action="AllDoctors" class="cta-btn">See Doctors</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    :root {
        --primary: #2196f3;
        --primary-dark: #1976d2;
        --primary-light: #bbdefb;
        --secondary: #0d47a1;
        --secondary-dark: #002171;
        --accent: #42a5f5;
        --light: #f5f5f5;
        --dark: #333333;
        --gray: #78909c;
        --light-gray: #eceff1;
    }

    /* Global styles */
    body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        color: var(--dark);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
        }

            .section-header h2::after {
                content: '';
                display: block;
                width: 80px;
                height: 4px;
                background-color: var(--primary);
                margin: 1rem auto 0;
            }

        .section-header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--gray);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

    /* Hero section styles */
    .hero {
        position: relative;
        height: 100vh;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        overflow: hidden;
        background-image: url('@Url.Content("~/images/images2/Slide1.jpg")');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
    }

    .hero-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(13, 71, 161, 0.9) 0%, rgba(13, 71, 161, 0.7) 50%, rgba(13, 71, 161, 0.4) 100%);
    }

    .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        max-width: 650px;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 3rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        margin-left: 8%;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero p {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .hero-buttons {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* Button styles */
    .primary-btn, .hero-btn, .cta-btn, .about-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: var(--primary);
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

        .primary-btn:hover, .hero-btn:hover, .cta-btn:hover, .about-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

    .secondary-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: transparent;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 0.95rem 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        border: 2px solid #ffffff;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

        .secondary-btn:hover {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

    .about-btn {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Stats section */
    .stats {
        padding: 3rem 0;
        background-color: var(--primary);
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .stats-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-number {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .stat-label {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Features section styles */
    .features {
        padding: 8rem 0;
        background-color: var(--light);
    }

    .feature-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        border-bottom: 4px solid transparent;
    }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin: 1rem 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

    .feature-icon {
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        height: 80px;
        width: 80px;
        line-height: 80px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.1);
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Services section styles */
    .services {
        padding: 8rem 0;
        background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .service-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .service-card {
        background-color: var(--light);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

        .service-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .service-card:hover::before {
                transform: scaleX(1);
            }

        .service-card h3 {
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin: 1rem 0;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

    .service-icon {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        height: 70px;
        width: 70px;
        line-height: 70px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.1);
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    }

    .service-link {
        display: inline-block;
        color: var(--primary);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

        .service-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .service-link i {
            margin-left: 5px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .service-link:hover i {
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

    /* Testimonials section */
    .testimonials {
        padding: 8rem 0;
        background-color: var(--light);
    }

    .testimonial-slider {
        display: flex;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
        position: relative;
    }

    .testimonial-item {
        min-width: 100%;
        padding: 0 1rem;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .testimonial-content {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 3rem;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
    }

        .testimonial-content::before {
            content: '\201C';
            font-size: 6rem;
            color: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.1);
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 20px;
            font-family: serif;
            line-height: 1;
        }

    .testimonial-rating {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #ffc107;
    }

    .testimonial-content p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--dark);
    }

    .testimonial-author {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .author-name {
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--secondary);
    }

    .author-title {
        color: var(--gray);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .testimonial-controls {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .testimonial-prev, .testimonial-next {
        background-color: var(--primary);
        color: #ffffff;
        border: none;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

        .testimonial-prev:hover, .testimonial-next:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

    /* About Us section styles */
    .about-us {
        padding: 8rem 0;
        background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .about-content {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 4rem;
        background-color: var(--light);
        padding: 3rem;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .about-text {
        flex: 1;
    }

        .about-text p {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--dark);
        }

    .about-image {
        flex: 1;
        text-align: center;
    }

        .about-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

            .about-image img:hover {
                transform: scale(1.03);
            }

    /* FAQ section styles - NEW DESIGN WITH TABS */
    .faq {
        padding: 8rem 0;
        background-color: var(--light);
    }

    .faq-tabs {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .faq-tab {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-light), #ffffff);
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .faq-checkbox {
        position: absolute;
        opacity: 0;
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .faq-label {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--secondary);
        cursor: pointer;
        position: relative;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

        .faq-label:hover {
            background-color: rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.05);
        }

    .faq-arrow {
        position: relative;
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
    }

        .faq-arrow::before,
        .faq-arrow::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .faq-arrow::before {
            top: 9px;
            left: 0;
            width: 20px;
            height: 2px;
        }

        .faq-arrow::after {
            top: 0;
            left: 9px;
            width: 2px;
            height: 20px;
        }

    .faq-checkbox:checked ~ .faq-label .faq-arrow::after {
        transform: rotate(90deg);
        opacity: 0;
    }

    .faq-content {
        max-height: 0;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
        color: var(--gray);
        background: white;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .faq-checkbox:checked ~ .faq-content {
        max-height: 300px;
        padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    }

    /* CTA Section */
    .cta {
        padding: 5rem 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .cta-content {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cta p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .cta-btn {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: var(--primary);
    }

        .cta-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

